<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="R" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Remit" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Remit,</orth> 1) to leave unpunished, to pardon: <bibl n="shak. mm 2.4.44" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. II, 4, 44</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 5.526.44" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 526</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 1.484" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. I, 484</bibl>.<lb />2) to give up, to resign: <cit><quote>will you have me, or your pearl again? Neither of either; I r. both twain,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.459" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 459</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>